      "layout": "The pages conform to a maximum content width, centered on a Canvas White background, creating a structured canvas. The hero section features a prominent, centered headline with a subtext below, allowing ample white space. Content sections typically alternate between left-aligned text blocks and right-aligned abstract graphics or key feature callouts. There's a consistent vertical rhythm of comfortable section gaps (often 32px or 40px). Navigation is a minimal top bar with ghost buttons, suggesting a more app-like or single-page experience.",
